=== Test 1: RHS evaluated at assignment time, not declaration order ===
Evaluating RHS of field a
Evaluating RHS of field c
Constructor start
Assigning b (no RHS in class)
Constructor end - a and c should be auto-initialized from RHS
Result: a=100 b=200 c=300

=== Test 2: Mixed RHS and non-RHS fields ===
Evaluating RHS of field x with value 1
Evaluating RHS of field z with value 3
Assigning y (only field without RHS)
x and z should auto-initialize from RHS
Result: x=10 y=999 z=30

=== Test 3: Class parameters with field initializers ===
Initializing f1, p1=5
Initializing f2, p2=7
Initializing f3
Result: p1=5 p2=7 f1=50 f2=140 f3=190
